</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="680C57A5578D759E4FF4BF3C324DAD14" pageId="0" pageNumber="21" type="selected specimen examined">
<paragraph id="BDF0FBF97A0848D468EB47DAD27AA7B7" pageId="0" pageNumber="21">Selected specimen examined.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2AD5BB7AF9C5B13BDC55E8F462313FD5" pageId="0" pageNumber="21">
<emphasis id="5FA64A0C4FDD45D30940D97A197F2D8E" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="21">China: Qinghai Province</emphasis>
: Kuen-Lun, Dolina r. 
<normalizedToken id="80D736AA1A6403D8B6A199550AC38FD0" originalValue="Sharagol’">Sharagol'</normalizedToken>
-dzhin, yr. Paidza-Tologoi, 11000 ft alt., pesch. 
<normalizedToken id="0E815787F16DE11658F15EDF55DBE937" originalValue="step’">step'</normalizedToken>
, 11 Jul 1894, 
